column5: Anybody have a lead on who does custom bimini tops around the GTA,got a new tracker,figure it might extend life of interior and extend fishing season.....any info would be appreciated..willing to trailer boat up north if need be............

larrys custom auto trim on russett ave oshawa,he does all kinds of things like that he did me a custom boat cover about 4 years ago ,he does cars boats rv's 905-725-4914 or 725-9325 give him a call,and let me know he has been in the business for 30 yrs  hope this helps
